Dialogue: 9,0:00:02.74,0:00:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece difícil!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Para de se rir de mim, Avó.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou apenas feliz em ver que você está bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava um pouco preocupado porque você levou muito tempo para se recuperar.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguarde.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou recebendo outra chamada.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:20.67,0:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, vou atender.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Até logo, vovó.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Bem, um...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso ficar na sua casa hoje à noite?
