Dialogue: 9,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\r}Eaah...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\r}Boa noite...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:37.64,0:02:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado novamente.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.81,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é um salvador de vidas.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Entre aí.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:43.61,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Você chegou no momento certo.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi alguns sons estranhos antes.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me assustaram.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quer comer algo?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:55.95,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheira delicioso!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:17.85,0:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O mesmo aconteceu\Ntambém quando eu estava tomando banho.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:25.15,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, vem logo!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Me pergunto o que será.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo pronto.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Arroz comum ba—{strawberry jam donut}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Você realmente passou pelo sistema de drenagem?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas por assustá-lo.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deve ter se sentido solitária.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:31.92,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Estava pensando em quantas vezes\Nnos veremos antes do fim,
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,e isso me fez querer vê-lo.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu desejo que tivéssemos paz.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teremos muitas \Oportunidades para isso.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:46.23,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos derrotar os Gauna e acabar com esta guerra.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.74,0:04:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Os sistemas de controle foram\Ninstalados, Dr. Shinatose.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho, Numi{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Você foi realmente útil.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fico honrado em ter podido ajudar.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:08.96,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me pergunto como ela sabe tanto sobre a pesquisa de Gauna de Ochiai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yure.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouvi que nossa nova arma está pronta.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda não, capitã.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro que posso mostrar resultados tangíveis.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,mas controlar as partes feitas de placenta está sendo difícil.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:30.36,0:05:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um teste de ativação agora\Nseria um pouco perigoso.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo levaria para aprimorá-la?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:37.99,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisaria de seis meses para repetir\Nestes experimentos de imitação placentária.{experiments relating to the imitation ability of placenta... i put shapechange, not sure whats better. pls suggest}
Dialogue: 9,0:05:42.03,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta arma é de extrema importância\Na nossa guerra contra o grande agrupamento de ninhos.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,O teste de ativação \)vai ocorrer conforme planejado.[T0]
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mas...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Como você desejar.[T1]
Dialogue: 9,0:06:01.85,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos agora testar uma formação mista de Type 18\NGarde com o novo Type 17 Tsugumori Mark 2.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação quadrada!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Santa... merda...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa aceleração.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:20.03,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma formação quadrada com o Tsugumori Mark 2 se revela bastante rápida.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:23.41,0:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,É bom ter perfeito o novo sistema de propulsão.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fala Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheguei um pouco atrasado, mas gostaria de participar da atividade.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou o novo piloto de Tsumugi,
Dialogue: 9,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato Mozuku.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Prazer em conhecer você.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa aceleração é louca.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunca nos alcançaríamos dela.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressionante.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, como você gera tração?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Eu realmente não sei.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seria legal se pudéssemos adaptá-lo aos Gardes.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Espero que você já tenha tudo\Nresolvido, Kunato{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.47,0:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, muitas coisas ainda estão incertas.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Acredite em mim.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:28.02,0:07:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Equipe de Gardes, agora tentarão entrar na formação com a cimera Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Desfaça-se da formação!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0].
Dialogue: 9,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos tentar.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tanikaze[T2]...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Essa mobilidade...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:56.38,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece que Tanikaze realmente está se adaptando bem com a cimera.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo, Samari?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu suponho.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:18.15,0:08:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Velocidade média para a formação mista\Nmais de oito vezes a regular Type 18.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda temos espaço para avançar.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Desempenho angular é \Mmais de dez vezes maior.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:27.37,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é louco.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze Nagate[T0].
Dialogue: 9,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:38.75,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que Tsumugi realmente gosta de você.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:43.26,0:08:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Espero que possamos nos entender\Nigual a vocês dois.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Um...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seja gentil com Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou seguro.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais por agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Até mais...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda há tempo.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,De acordo.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Um...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}Olá...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá, Tanikaze{**-san}.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso te incomodar novamente sobre algo?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:31.89,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,De boa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:40.02,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}100 Atrações de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:37.06,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Pipa Agendada para Manutenção
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.02,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Novo Hangar 7
Dialogue: 9,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,O mapa da pipa te ajudou?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, enormemente.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado novamente.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:49.50,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No entanto, isso se trata de algo completamente diferente.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou ouvindo.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou procurando por propriedades com muitos tubulações fora de serviço.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:00.26,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, eu não sabia que você tinha tanto interesse em saneamento.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizei algumas pesquisas preliminares.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode dar uma olhada nisso?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta área na parede externa ficaria ótima.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.73,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}Algo em silêncio, se possível...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Parede externa?!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:21.99,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
