Dialogue: 9,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou de volta.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Você chegou cedo.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fico aliviado por ter dado uma chave extra.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabia que, se você estiver de acordo,
Dialogue: 9,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}você poderia ficar aqui com—
Dialogue: 9,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A mappa do tubo?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu olhei para o lugar\NI'm moving to hoje.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:27.71,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, ok.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Está aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}E isso é...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:37.39,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,O quarto da Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai viver na parede externa!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Então...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quer mudar para lá comigo?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:51.45,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas se você quiser.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas se eu quiser?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é a parede externa.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:04.33,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode ter permissão para viver lá.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,mas um piloto comum como eu
Dialogue: 9,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,não está permitido viver em lugar tão luxuoso.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe com isso!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:17.14,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Diz aqui que posso ter\Nalguém morando comigo!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Olhe.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:29.11,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Eu queria consultar você primeiro...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só tive um tempo livre hoje... e você sabe...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro, por que não?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá juntos.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lá.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,É bem longe da estação.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:01.06,0:15:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Há uma linha direta para o setor militar no fundo.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode vê-lo agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Este lugar é ótimo!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro que sim!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou chamar Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenha a respiração, Izana.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Há poeira nos tubos.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela vai expulsá-la.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:43.39,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, teríamos que limpar aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:54.19,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Qualquer problema além da poeira?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nenhum.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:58.99,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Os tubos são bem espaçosos, então chegar até aqui foi muito confortável.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é bom.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Algum problema, Tanikaze{**-san}?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Você parece um pouco triste.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:22.93,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Você ainda está acordado?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:27.14,0:16:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não preciso realmente dormir.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:31.02,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Posso dormir se decidir, mas...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou bem estranho.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:40.16,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontrei isso na parede no fundo.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Viu escaravelho de madeira!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Não tão alto.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que Izana está dormindo.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Um...
Dialogue: 9,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso tocá-lo?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:57.13,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas seja cuidadoso.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:00.43,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que vejo um.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Igual.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,É bonito.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Peço desculpas.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu teria deixado passar de qualquer forma.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:22.62,0:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que o caranguejo nos vê como predadores assustadores\Nque ele nunca poderia comunicar com.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, acho que é verdade.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.55,0:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Não seria possível que estamos simplesmente muito diferentes\Npara nos comunicarmos em qualquer nível?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\r}{\i1}Hoshijiro...{\i0}
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\r}Ei...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0]?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha a hora.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Devemos ir dormir.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\r}Tá...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem então, boa noite.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Um... Eu...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Quero dormir com você, Tanikaze{**-san}!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é um não?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Está bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um planeta anão pirata passando por aqui.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A distância atual é de 180.000 quilômetros.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso teria sido uma ótima oportunidade\Npara mineração de matérias-primas.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava convencido de que íamos miná-la\Nquando a capitã ordenou um curso
Dialogue: 9,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,que nos levaria ao planeta anão.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:32.41,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O emissor está na última fase de preparação.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pessoal não essencial deve evacuar imediatamente os locais.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:38.25,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Linha de suprimento de partículas Heigus nominal.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nenhuma interferência detectada.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Equipamento de refluxo de partículas Heigus e\Nvalvulas de proteção contra fluxo contrário funcionando.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pessoal para os testes foi deslocado\Npara as últimas ajustes.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece... não como eu esperava.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece um Gauna.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:57.44,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Utilizamos a capacidade do placentário de imitar qualquer coisa para finalizar o dispositivo.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Emissor de Raio Gravitônico...
Dialogue: 9,0:20:07.86,0:20:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma das armas maravilhosas {\alpha&HFF&\fscx20}...{\r}do cientista Ochiai...
Dialogue: 9,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Operadores, vocês me ouvem?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:14.66,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Conecte a supply de partícula Heigus.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seja cauteloso.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Conectando suprimento de partícula Heigus.{is that a giant molex cable}
Dialogue: 9,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ligação estabelecida.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Abrindo suprimento.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Iniciando ativação do emissor.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:45.94,0:20:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Abrindo válvulas de segurança.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ativando emissor.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,O emissor está ativo.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alveje o planeta anão errático.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Solução de tiro alcançada.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pronto para disparar.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:16.85,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparo.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Emissor de Raios Gravitônicos...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,disparando.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Emissão bem-sucedida.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:01.98,0:22:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as matérias dentro de 100 quilômetros\Ndo eixo de emissão foram aniquiladas.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:09.74,0:22:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Capitã?
Dialogue: 9,0:22:14.53,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnífico.
