Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:35.35,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo estiver condenado à destruição,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:35.35,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]aa kuchiteku sekai naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:38.85,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:38.85,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]chiriyuku sadame naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:44.44,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que viveria?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:44.44,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]nani wo shinjite ikireba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:50.11,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:50.11,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se não fosse por ti, eu nunca sentiria dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.53,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu nunca teria sentido esta dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.53,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}quebrando meu coração de forma dolorosa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:00.12,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}arrancando meu coração em pedaços
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:00.12,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer a dor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.87,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}é uma requiem grosseira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.87,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.33,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando até lá
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.33,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}não foi há muito tempo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.17,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.17,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requiem ininterrupto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.09,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e até agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.09,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ainda assim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:11.80,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:11.80,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}buscando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:15.22,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:15.22,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}desde agora em diante
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.22,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}para você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.22,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que diz respeito a você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.85,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.85,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também da alegria de nos encontrarmos
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:24.56,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o calor da sua presença
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:24.56,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o passar do seu ser aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:28.77,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e o tempo que você esteve aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:28.77,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Estou lembrando de tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.86,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.86,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:35.61,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:35.61,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o registro do mar profundo que eu vi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.61,0:23:39.33,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.61,0:23:39.33,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}até mesmo as cicatrizes restantes no meu peito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:43.71,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu carregarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:43.71,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}vou caminhar com todas as minhas forças
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:50.71,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e seguir meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:50.71,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu vou percorrer esta estrada
